Version 1.1 has been releases.  Several new features include:

* FileAssert: tests both text and binary files.
* OrderTestSuite: executes the tests in an alphabetical order.
* TestSetup: always executes the tearDown method.

website: <http://junit-addons.sourceforge.net>
